--
Running the application on port 8081:
mvn spring-boot:run

--
Available endpoints:

http://localhost:8081/signup

http://localhost:8081/register/{token}
Example: http://localhost:8081/register/eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJNSXhxTVVxZXFGdzZvcUp6MzBsQjJPRmxOVWd5ZEUiLCJleHAiOjE3Mjk4NzYzNzZ9.hZcHnVlpAjWEdcM8F8S5xEruYipMVyCmrSK49JUKDMZo9aUNjtdiFMz1MXkIdY_LLi3jFa-tUCPzR1CNDVuCUg

http://localhost:8081/users/{userId}
Example: http://localhost:8081/users/V16l2CVctDB7kMTzidAjgWfkiUxLZh